tafsir[3]{c,v,t}:
  37,54,"His believing companion will say to his companions of the people of Paradise: “Take a look with me; let us see the outcome of that companion of mine who used to deny the resurrection.”"
  37,55,"So he will take a look and see his companion in the middle of hell."
  37,74,"Except for those whom Allah chose to believe in Him and His oneness; they were saved from the punishment which was the outcome of the disbelieving rejectors."